'''Afrika Borwa''' goba '''Repabliki le Afrika-Borwa''' (Republic of South Africa) ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. ''Afrika Borwa'' e borwa ba [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Borwa ba Afrika|Borwa Ba Afrika]].

''Afrika Borwa'' e agišane le : 
* [[Namibia]] (leboa bodikela),
* [[Botswana]](leboa),
* [[Zimbabwe]] (leboa bohlabela),
* [[Mozambique]] (bohlabela), le
* [[Swaziland]], le
* [[Lesotho]].

Afrika Borwa ke leloko la [[Commonwealth of Nations]].

Go tloga ka [[1999]], [[Thabo Mbeki]] ebile mopresidente wa lesome pedi was Afrika Borwa. Pele ga Thabo Mbheki, Ntate [[Nelson Mandela]] e be e le mopresidente.

== Dipolelo ==
Afrika borwa e nale [[Maleme a Afrika Borwa|dipolelo tše lešome tee]] tša semmušo elego [[Sezulu]], [[Sethosa]], [[Afrikaans]], [[Sepedi]], [[Setswana]], [[Seisimane|Seisemane]], [[Sesotho]], [[Setsonga]], [[Seswati]], [[Sevenda]] le [[Sendebele]]. Afrika Borwa e nale dipolelo tša goswana le Fanagalo, Selobedu, Setebele sa Leboa le SeSan tšeo dibolelwago efela ese dipolelo tša semmušo.

== Diporofense ==
Go tloga ka 1994 ge kgethollo e fela, diporense tša Afrika Borwa di senyane, elego

* [[Kapa Bohlabela]]
* [[Free State]]
* [[Gauteng]]
* [[KwaZulu Natala]]
* [[Limpopo]]
* [[Mpumalanga]]
* [[Kapa Leboa]]
* [[Leboa Bohlabela Transvaal|Leboa Bohlabela (Transvaal)]]
* [[Kapa Bodikela]]

== Bodumedi ==
Go ya ka dipala tša setšhaba tša ngwaga wa 2001, 79.7% ya badudi ba Afrika Borwa ke [[Sekriste|bakriste]].

== Badudi ==
Afrika Borwa e nale badudi bao ekabago dimillione tše 47. Go lekanetšwa gore 79.5 yad badudi ke [[Batho Batsho|batho batsho]], 9.2% ke [[makgowa]], ge 8.9 ele [[Batho Ba Mmala|batho ba mmala]], 2.5% ke [[maIndia]].

